 The number of speaker signals used may vary, but to align with with the
 definition for babble should be between three and six.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
For Generation
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It is generally desirable in testing to be able to present noise at different
 
\begin_inset ERT
